1.title: Episode #1.1
1.plot: The Premiere Episode of That Hashtag Show!. This week includes Free Comic Book Day and Guillermo Del Toro discussing Justice League Dark.

2.title: Episode #1.2
2.plot: In this weeks episode we catch up with Chris Carter about the X-Files, learn about the XBOX One and PS4, and Jeff gives you the lowdown on what comics he thinks you should read.

3.title: That Hashtag Show Goes to E3 2013
3.plot: Jeff May arrives at E3 and wanders the floor while rocking out to the Ducktales theme.

4.title: WI-Fi Hangs Out with Mario & Luigi
4.plot: Hashtag Correspondent Wi-Fi (Adrienne Wieder-Finch) meets Mario and Luigi and gets to play some Mario Kart 8.

5.title: Curiousjoi Checks Out the X-Box One Controller
5.plot: Curiousjoi (Joi Tanner) takes a look at the Xbox One Controller.

6.title: That Hashtag Show: Episode 3
6.plot: This week on That Hashtag Show: Aaron Pita sits in for Jeff May and fills you in on Man of Steel, Microsoft's 180, and The Amazing Spiderman 2. Jeff, Wi-Fi and Curious Joi check out E3 and bring us back some gaming goodness.

7.title: E3 Best of Jeff May Edition
7.plot: The Best of Jeff May as he ventures around the floor of E3.

8.title: Wi-Fi Talks to Yaya Han Cosplay Ambassador at Anime Expo 2013
8.plot: That Hashtag Show correspondent Wi-Fi (Adrienne Wieder-Finch) interviews Cosplay Ambassador Yaya Han at the Anime Expo 2013 and finds out what her favorite cosplay costume is.

9.title: That Hashtag Show's Jeff May Arrives at San Diego Comic Con 2013
9.plot: That Hashtag Show is at #SDCC keep up with us all weekend as we bring you the latest from San Diego!.

10.title: Jeff May Interviews Eisner Nominee Sara Richard (My Little Pony)
10.plot: Jeff May talks to Eisner nominated Sara Richard about her book Kitty and Dino.

11.title: Jeff May Interviews Reilly Brown, Power Play Comic Book Artist
11.plot: Jeff from That Hashtag Show interviews Comic Book artist Reilly Brown and talks about his new digital comic Power play, now on ComiXology.

12.title: Wi-Fi Talks to Lonstermash
12.plot: WiFi met up with the best there is, Wolverine.

13.title: Exclusive John Barrowman Interview at SDCC 2013
13.plot: Jeff May from That Hashtag Show interviews John Barrowman about Arrow, not crashing the SDCC Arrow panel, and who should replace Matt Smith as the Doctor in the next season of Doctor Who.

14.title: Aaron Pita Interviews Walter Jones (The Original Black Power Ranger)
14.plot: Aaron Interviews Walter E. Jones, the Original Black Power Ranger. They talk about the 20th Anniversary of Power Rangers and what Walter's up to now.

15.title: Jeff May Interviews Edward James Olmos
15.plot: That Hashtag Show's Jeff May Interviews Battlestar Galactica's Edward James Olmos about his charitable works.

16.title: Jeff May Interviews Comic Book Legend George Perez
16.plot: That Hashtag Show's Jeff May interviews Legendary Comic Book artist and writer, George Perez. They talk about a great cause that helps out Comic Book Creators from the Past, the Hero Initiative.

17.title: Batman V. Superman: The Fans Decide at Comic-Con 2013
17.plot: Sarah Carey, Jeff May, and Aaron Pita hit the streets of San Diego during SDCC and ask the tough question, Who would win in a fight between Superman and Batman . . . or between Aaron Pita and a backpack.

18.title: Episode #1.18
18.plot: In this weeks episode Aaron and Jeff discuss GTAV, ios7, Vin Diesel as a talking Tree, and Joss Whedon being airlifted in to rewrite scripts.

19.title: UD Replicas Leather Jacket Cosplay
19.plot: Back at SDCC Sarah Carey from The Price of Admission Podcast spoke with David Pea of UD Replicas and got a look at some of their newest outfits based on Man of Steel, Batman: TDKR, and KISS.

20.title: Independent Comic Book Guns A' Blazin' Release Party
20.plot: Sean Novicki was onsite at The Comic Bug to talk to Mike Wellman and Raphael Navarro about their self published comic book, Guns A' Blazin'.

21.title: 24 Hour Comic Book Day at the Comic Bug
21.plot: Joe and Jessica hang out at The Comic Bug in Manhattan Beach, CA for 24 Hour Comic Book Day. Participants are given 24 hours to create a 24 page comic book.

22.title: Episode #1.22
22.plot: Jeff and Aaron discuss Harrison Ford's career choices, Robert Kirkman ruining lives, and Aaron lures Jeff into his sex dungeon.

23.title: Jeff May Talks to Stan Lee at Comikaze 2013
23.plot: Jeff May talks to the Generalissimo himself, Stan Lee.

24.title: Jeff May Interviews AMC's Comic Book Men
24.plot: The Comic Book Men took a few minutes out of their day to talk to Jeff.

25.title: Jeff May Interviews WWE's Rob Van Dam
25.plot: Jeff talks to the one and only Whole F'N Show, ROB VAN DAM about his comic Twisted Perception - Soldiers of Karma.

26.title: That Hashtag Show: Episode 8
26.plot: This week, Jeff and Aaron discuss casting rumors for Ant-Man, Steven Spielberg nuking fridges, and Batman driving around in a Cadillac.

27.title: How to Make Monsters with Stan Winston School
27.plot: Jessica interviews Matt Winston about the Stan Winston School. Learn how to make Monsters by the Masters of FX.

28.title: Jeff May Interviews Comic Book Artist Mike Mayhew at Wonder Con 2014
28.plot: Jeff May talks to Comic artist Mike Mayhew, known for his work on the currently running The Star Wars, from Dark Horse Comics and his previous work with Marvel and D.C. Comics.

29.title: Stephanie Pressman Interviews Assassins Creed's Cas Anvar at Wonder Con 2104
29.plot: Stephanie Pressman talks to Actor Cas Anvar, known for voicing Altair in Assassin's Creed, Peteen in Star Wars: Clone Wars, and for his role as Ibrahim Al-Munin on CBS's Intelligence.

1.title: Jessica Heidenreich talks to UD Replica at Wonder Con 2014
1.plot: That Hashtag Show's Jessica Heidenreich talks to David Pea from UD Replicas about their various collections including, Man of Steel, Batman (The Dark Knight), G.I.Joe, and their newly released My Little Pony line of Leather wear.

2.title: That Hashtag Show Highlights of Wonder Con 2014
2.plot: Check out some of our highlights from WonderCon 2014.

3.title: That Hashtag Show Goes to E3 2014
3.plot: That Hashtag Show was at E3 2014. Check out a brief Montage of our trip. Make sure to subscribe to our channel so you don't miss our interviews and sneak peeks from the show floor.

4.title: Cosplay: VertVixen Talks to YaYa Han
4.plot: Hashtag Correspondent Alicia got the chance to talk to Master Cosplayer Yaya Han at Anime Expo 2014.

5.title: Wi-Fi Learns About Bushiroad
5.plot: From the vault: Check out Wi-Fi (Adrienne Wieder-Finch) talk about the Collectible Card Game, Bushiroad at Anime Expo 2013.

6.title: The Cast of Dragon Ball Z Talks Battle of Gods
6.plot: Marissa Floro sat down with the cast of Dragon Ball Z: Battle of Gods to talk about the film. They talk about the characters they relate to the best and the production experience.

7.title: The Cast of Dragon Ball Z Share Funny Behind the Scene Pranks
7.plot: Sean Schemmell (Goku) shares a couple stories on how Christopher Sabat (Vegeta) and Justin Cook (Dende) played pranks on him while they were recording Dragon Ball Z.

8.title: Dragon Ball Z: Battle of Gods Movie Premiere Red Carpet Interviews
8.plot: Chris Hawley from the band Walls That Talk went to the DBZ: Battle of Gods Movie Premiere and got a chance to talk with the stars of the film Sean Schemmel (Goku), Christopher Sabat (Vegeta), Kyle Hebert (Gohan), Mike McFarland (Master Roshi).

9.title: Dragon Ball Z: What Would the Cast Do with Their Dragon Ball Wish?
9.plot: At the Dragon Ball Z: Battle of Gods Red Carpet we asked the cast if they had all 7 Dragon Balls, what would they wish for?

10.title: Doctor Who: Does Paul McGann Have Any Advice for Peter Capaldi
10.plot: We sat down with 8th Doctor, Paul McGann and he talks about coming back for the 50th Anniversary, advice to Peter Capaldi, and some of his favorite villains from the series Doctor Who.

11.title: Wi-Fi Talks to Doctor Who Cosplayer
11.plot: Wi-FI (Adrienne Wider-Finch) caught up with a few Doctor Who cosplayers and asked them about their favorite show.

12.title: Justin Wong Talks Ultra Street Fighter IV
12.plot: Marissa Floro talks to Justin Wong about Ultra Street Fighter IV.

13.title: That Hashtag Show Goes to Power Morphicon 2014
13.plot: Joseph Deckelmeier explores Power Morphicon 2014. He talks to former Power Rangers and even tries to test their Power Ranger knowledge. Full interviews coming soon.

14.title: Ari Boyland Talks Power Rangers RPM at Power Morphicon 2014
14.plot: Joe caught up with Ari Boyland ('Flynn', Power Rangers R.P.M). They talk about the direction of the RPM season, test Ari's RPM knowledge, and talks about Ari's new film, 'Blood Punch'. Watch the full 'Blood Punch' trailer at the end of the video. There's appearance by former Power Rangers: R.P.M. cast members.

15.title: Austin St. John Talks Power Rangers Dino Charge at Power Morphicon 2014
15.plot: We caught up with Austin St. John at Power Morphicon 2014. He talks about his experience in the early years, his possible return to the franchise in Dino Charge and if he's coming back for the movie in 2016. We also test Austin's knowledge on his season.

16.title: Power Rangers SPD Cast Interview at Power Morphicon 2014
16.plot: Joe Deckelmeier talked to the cast and Executive Producer of Power Rangers SPD at Power Morphicon 2014. They all give great insight to their season of Power Rangers and they catch us up on what they're doing now.

17.title: Marissa Talks to the Team from Killer Instinct
17.plot:
Know what this is about?
 Be the first one to add a plot.

18.title: VR Trooopers Brad Hawkins Interview at Power Morphicon 2014
18.plot: Joseph Deckelmeier interviewed Brad Hawkins at Power Morphicon 2014 about his experience on VR Troopers and his early casting as the White Ranger. He also talks about voicing the Gold Ranger on Power Rangers Zeo and his new, critically acclaimed film, 'BOYHOOD', and takes the VR Trooper Quiz. Watch the trailer for 'Boyhood' at the end of the video.

19.title: That Hashtag Newsfeed Week 9/22/14
19.plot: We're bringing you the latest trending news in Geek-Pop Culture. Alicia Bellamy (@Vertvixen) takes us through the weeks featured news. THIS WEEK IN GEEK NEWS: We give an update on the Deadpool film, the Executive Producer of the Power Rangers reboot movies exit, a special guest star on the Christmas Special of Doctor Who, and a Supergirl TV show.

20.title: Power Rangers Super Megaforce's Ciara Hanna Has Advice for the Dino Charge Cast
20.plot: We went to the Green Ranger vs. Blue Rangers Basketball Game for charity and caught up with Gia, the Yellow Super Megaforce Ranger, Ciara Hanna. Ciara talks about the experience working with the Legendary Rangers, takes a quiz about the Super Megaforce season, and give her advice to the Dino Charge Rangers.

21.title: The Cast of Power Rangers Zeo Interviews from Power Morphicon 2014
21.plot: Joseph Deckelmeier (@SupermanJP) got the chance to interview Steve Cardenas (Rocky), Catherine Sutherland (Kat), and Nakia Burrise (Tanya) from Power Rangers Zeo! They talk about the Power Rangers Zeo season and catch us up on what they're up to now.

22.title: That Hashtag Newsfeed: Geek News Week of 9/29/14
22.plot: THIS WEEK IN GEEK NEWS: What to expect from the X-Men: Apocalypse movie, Fantastic Four movie update. Also in gaming news Blizzard cancels Titan?.

23.title: Power Rangers Samurai: Hector David Jr. Takes the Power Rangers Quiz
23.plot: Joe talked to Hector David Jr., Mike, the Green Samurai Ranger at Green vs. Blue Ranger Basketball Game. He talks about the charity event, coming back to Super Megaforce, and takes a small quiz on his season.

24.title: Days of the Dead Horror Convention 2014
24.plot: We went to the Days of the Dead Horror Convention in Los Angeles and talked to horror legend Sid Haig and Smallville star, John Schnieder.

25.title: Reign of Terror Haunted House
25.plot: We sent Sarah out to check out the best Haunted Houses around the nation. First stop, the Reign of Terror in Thousand Oaks, CA. The Reign of Terror Haunted House has been around for 15 years and gets better every year.

26.title: Power Rangers Time Force Cast Interview & Quiz from Power Morphicon 2014
26.plot: Erin Cahill (Jen, Pink Time Force Ranger), Jason Faunt (Wes, Red Time Force Ranger), and Dan Southworth (Eric, Quantum Ranger), all talked about their season and returns. They also take a small quiz to test their Power Ranger knowledge.

27.title: That Hashtag Newsfeed: Geek News Week of 10/6/14 (Iron Man 4, Doctor Strange, Star Wars & More)
27.plot: THIS WEEK IN GEEK NEWS: Robert Downey Jr. wants Mel Gibson to direct, Joaquin Phoenix and Doctor Strange update, Star Wars news, and the Universal Monsters shared universe.

28.title: Power Rangers Mystic Force: Richard Brancatisano (Xander) Takes the Power Rangers Quiz
28.plot: Joseph Deckelmeier talked to Richard Brancastisano, (Xander, Green Mystic Force Ranger) about his season and what he's doing now. Richie B. also takes the Power Ranger quiz on his season.

29.title: Highlights of the Queen Mary: Dark Harbor 2014 Haunted Mazes
29.plot: We sent Alicia for the Queen Mary's Dark Harbor for some fun and scares. We check out a couple of the mazes and saw the sights. Here's a highlight of what she experienced.

30.title: Bandai Namco Talks Power Rangers Super Megaforce (Nintendo 3DS)
30.plot: Mark Religioso from Bandai Namco gives us info for Power Rangers Super Megaforce for Nintendo 3DS at Power Morphicon 2014.. Power Rangers Super Megaforce comes out Oct. 28, 2014.

31.title: That Hashtag News Feed: Geek News Week of 10/13/14 (RDJ/Iron Man 4, Star Wars, Daredevil & More)
31.plot: THIS WEEK IN GEEK NEWS Robert Downey Jr. and Iron Man 4 Update, James Earl Jones Returning as Darth Vader, Spider-Man and the Avengers possibly teaming up on the big screen, and our first looks at Netflix's Daredevil, and Professor Zoom.

32.title: Christopher Khayman Lee from Power Rangers in Space Interview (Power Morphicon 2014)
32.plot: Joseph had a chance to talk to the Red Space Ranger, Christopher Khayman Lee about his season of Power Rangers, his new comic book, and a little PRiS quiz.

33.title: Highlights from Los Angeles Haunted Hayride 2014
33.plot: We sent our Horror Correspondent, Sarah Carey to see what all the buzz was about for the Los Angeles Haunted Hayride. The highlights she came back with did not disappoint.

34.title: Power Rangers Lightspeed Rescue Cast Interview (Power Morphicon 2014)
34.plot: Joseph caught up with the cast of Power Rangers Lightspeed Rescue (Sean C.W. Johnson (Carter), Keith Robinson (Joel), Rhett Fisher (Ryan), and Ron Rogge (Cap. Mitchel). He talks to them about their season and what they've been up to.

35.title: Power Rangers Fans: WE NEED YOUR HELP!
35.plot: This year we'll be at Stan Lee's Comikazee and talking to Past and Present Power Rangers. Leave a video question or submit your question in the comment below for a chance to get your questions answered by the Rangers.

36.title: That Hashtag Newsfeed: Geek News Week of 10/20/14 (DC Comics Movie News, RDJ in Cap. 3 & More)
36.plot: THIS WEEK IN GEEK NEWS: Alicia gives us the run down on what we can expect to see from DC Comics and Warner Bros, Captain America 3 with Robert Downey Jr. and Civil War, The Death of Wolverine, and casting rumors.

37.title: Power Rangers Fan Film 'The Ranger's Matt Jayson Interview
37.plot: Joseph talked to Matt Jayson, creator of the acclaimed Power Rangers Fan Film 'The Ranger' at Power Morphicon 2014.

38.title: Jessica Talks to Spider-Man Cosplayer Zach Luna
38.plot: Jessica Heidenreich talks to Spider-Man cosplayer, Zach Luna at Free Comic Book Day from the Comic Bug in Manhattan Beach.

39.title: Power Rangers SPD Cast Take a Quiz on Their Season
39.plot: The cast of Power Rangers SPD take a fun quiz about their season of Power Rangers.

40.title: The Cast of Power Rangers Zeo Take a Quiz on Their Season
40.plot: At Power Morphicon 2014 we quizzed former Power Rangers, Steve Cardenas (Rocky), Catherine Sutherland (Kat), and Nakia Burrise (Tanya) on MMPR, Power Rangers Zeo, and Power Rangers Turbo.

41.title: John Schneider Talks About Smothered the Movie at the Days of the Dead Horror Convention
41.plot: Sarah Carey interviewed Jonathan Kent himself, John Schneider. John talks about his latest directorial project, Smothered, a horror- comedy starring horror legends.

42.title: That Hashtag Newsfeed: Geek News of 10/27/14 (Age of Ultron, Marvel's Surprise Event, & More)
42.plot: Joseph gives us the rundown about Marvel's surprise announcement, Avengers: Age of Ultron, Sunset Overdrive, The Evolve Big Alpha Weekend, the Walking Dead video game and spin off, Lex Luthor in Suicide Squad.

43.title: Lulu: League of Legends Cosplay Interview (Anime Expo 2014)
43.plot: Alicia finds out how long and what it took Alexia to cosplay as Lulu from League of Legends at Anime Expo 2014.

44.title: Ernie Hudson Talks Ghostbusters 3
44.plot: We caught up with Ernie Hudson at the Saturn Awards and he gave us insight to Ghostbusters 3 and other Paranormal Films.

45.title: The Power Rangers Lightspeed Rescue Cast Takes a Quiz on Their Season
45.plot: At Power Morphicon 2014 we tested the cast of Power Rangers Lightspeed Rescue (Keith Robinson, Sean C.W. Johnson, Ron Rogge, and Rhett Fisher) on their knowledge of their season.

46.title: That Hashtag Show's at Stan Lee's Comikaze 2014
46.plot: Stay tuned to our channel for more videos including guest interviews, comic creators, panels, announcements, cosplayers, and more from Stan Lee's Comikaze 2014

imdb.title: That Hashtag Show
plot: _That Hashtag Show_ (qv) brings you the latest trending topics in geek pop-culture. They bring you coverage from the hottest conventions and geek events.
